[[File:Aberrant spectre icon.png|left]]
'''Aberrant spectres''' are [[Slayer monsters]] that require level 60 [[Slayer]] to kill. To avoid stat drain during combat with one, equip a [[nose peg]] or [[slayer helmet]]. They frequently drop large numbers of [[Herbs|grimy herbs]] and [[herb seed]]s. Because of this, bringing a [[herb sack]] and [[seed box]] when killing them is recommended.

[[Deviant spectre]]s, found in the [[Catacombs of Kourend]], can be killed in their place if you are assigned aberrant spectres.

